              Dream Beneath<br />the Goan Sky
            </h2>

            <p
              class="mt-6 max-w-lg text-white/90 md:text-lg md:leading-relaxed"
            >
              Cozy A-Frame huts and magical open-sky bathrooms create the
              perfect getaway for relaxation, adventure, and unforgettable
              memories.
            </p>

            <div class="mt-4 sm:mt-8">
              <a
