                Welcome to Luma!
              </h2>

              <div class="mt-4 text-base-content/90 md:mt-12">
                <p>
                  Welcome to Luma, a tranquil retreat tucked away in the heart
                  of South Goa. Our nine A-Frame huts blend rustic charm with a
                  touch of magic—each featuring a private open-sky bathroom for
                  showering under the stars.
                </p>
                <p class="mt-4">
                  Just a short hop from the coast, we offer a peaceful escape
                  surrounded by nature, perfect for those seeking simplicity and
                  serenity in one of India's most beloved destinations.
                </p>
                <p class="mt-4">
                  Unplug, unwind, and let South Goa's magic wash over you.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
